<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 12:12:25 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>ADL 称自加沙战争爆发以来美国反犹太主义事件增加了 300% 以上</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/antisemitic-incidents-in-u-s-up-over-300-since-start-of-gaza-war-adl-says/0000018b-c85a-d485-ab9b-ec7babcf0000</link><description>10月7日至11月7日期间发生了832起事件——平均每天28起。其中多起事件发生在美国东北部，其中112起发生在大学校园</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 12:00:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/antisemitic-incidents-in-u-s-up-over-300-since-start-of-gaza-war-adl-says/0000018b-c85a-d485-ab9b-ec7babcf0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争使以色列创作者与欧洲国际电影节之间的关系紧张</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/gaza-war-strains-ties-between-israeli-creators-and-european-international-film-fests/0000018b-c834-d485-ab9b-ec75990a0000</link><description>由于斯德哥尔摩电影节取消邀请以色列电视节目创作者，艺术总监对支持巴勒斯坦的抗议表示赞赏，并表示他们“必须表明立场”，以色列公共广播公司与电影节断绝了关系</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 11:36:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/gaza-war-strains-ties-between-israeli-creators-and-european-international-film-fests/0000018b-c834-d485-ab9b-ec75990a0000</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩对以色列北部的袭击加剧；真主党发射反坦克导弹后造成人员伤亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article-live/idf-warns-hezbollah-amid-escalation-in-north-source-cites-progress-in-hostage-deal/0000018b-c640-d485-ab9b-ee71f3c80006</link><description>以色列国防军称，从黎巴嫩发射的迫击炮弹落在空旷地区 ■ 美国称袭击了叙利亚境内与哈马斯有关的目标 ■ 以色列军队确认两名士兵在周日加沙战斗中丧生 ■ 巴勒斯坦报道：加沙的圣城医院和希法医院被关闭■ 以色列国防军发言人：哈马斯已失去对加沙北部的控制 ■ 至少 1,200 名以色列人在哈马斯大屠杀中丧生，239 名人质在加沙被扣，40 人下落不明 ■ 哈马斯管理的加沙卫生部：自战斗开始以来已有 11,078 人死亡</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 11:24:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article-live/idf-warns-hezbollah-amid-escalation-in-north-source-cites-progress-in-hostage-deal/0000018b-c640-d485-ab9b-ee71f3c80006</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡愿意诉诸珍珠港来逃避对以色列困境的责任</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-willing-to-resort-to-pearl-harbor-to-evade-responsiblity-for-israels-plight/0000018b-c82a-dadd-abfb-eafe69820000</link><description>在周日接受美国有线电视新闻网采访时，内塔尼亚胡反驳说，罗斯福没有被要求对日本在夏威夷的袭击负责。罗斯福也没有将装满现金的手提箱转移给日本海军，也没有忽视自己的将军们长达数月的警告</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 11:23:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-willing-to-resort-to-pearl-harbor-to-evade-responsiblity-for-israels-plight/0000018b-c82a-dadd-abfb-eafe69820000</guid></item><item><title>希法医院的悲剧：以色列在加沙战争中面临的最大道德挑战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/al-shifa-hospital-israels-biggest-moral-challenge-in-the-gaza-war/0000018b-c45b-db2f-a7cb-dedba4900000</link><description>希法不仅是加沙最大的医院，也是一个大型难民营，据以色列称，它是哈马斯领导层活动的中央总部。直到最近，该医疗中心仍是以色列-哈马斯战争的核心，以色列医生每月进行 50 次手术。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 11:00:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/al-shifa-hospital-israels-biggest-moral-challenge-in-the-gaza-war/0000018b-c45b-db2f-a7cb-dedba4900000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡让以色列在加沙战争问题上与拜登发生冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-sets-israel-on-collision-course-with-biden-over-gaza-war/0000018b-c800-df10-adeb-deb6f5aa0000</link><description>总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡认为，加沙的长期战争将减轻批评并让他继续掌权。更重要的是，他认为这将使他能够分散责任，摆脱对 10 月 7 日灾难的所有个人责任</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 10:41:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-sets-israel-on-collision-course-with-biden-over-gaza-war/0000018b-c800-df10-adeb-deb6f5aa0000</guid></item><item><title>美国前情报总监克拉珀：摧毁哈马斯就意味着摧毁加沙地带</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/ex-u-s-intel-director-clapper-destroying-hamas-means-destroying-gaza-strip/0000018b-c7ea-df10-adeb-d7fe84e80000</link><description>詹姆斯·克拉珀告诉《国土报》，如果真主党发动袭击，美国必须进行干预，哈马斯和伊斯兰国一样邪恶，而且短期内看不到两国解决方案</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 09:59:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/ex-u-s-intel-director-clapper-destroying-hamas-means-destroying-gaza-strip/0000018b-c7ea-df10-adeb-d7fe84e80000</guid></item><item><title>英国内政大臣因批评警方对亲巴勒斯坦抗议者“宽大处理”而被解雇</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/u-k-home-secretary-fired-after-attacking-police-leniency-on-pro-palestinian-protesters/0000018b-c7eb-dadd-abfb-e7ff91830000</link><description>在上周针对警察的一次极不寻常的袭击中，布雷弗曼表示，伦敦警方无视“亲巴勒斯坦暴徒”的违法行为。在极右翼抗议者与警察发生扭打并试图对抗大规模亲巴勒斯坦游行后，苏纳克面临着越来越大的解雇她的压力</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 09:47:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/u-k-home-secretary-fired-after-attacking-police-leniency-on-pro-palestinian-protesters/0000018b-c7eb-dadd-abfb-e7ff91830000</guid></item><item><title>真主党的危险举动可能会在以色列北部引发第二次全面战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/hezbollahs-dangerous-plays-liable-to-spur-second-war-front-in-israels-north/0000018b-c555-dadd-abfb-e7ffb4530000</link><description>以色列将不得不考虑是否能够通过表现出克制来遏制黎巴嫩正在进行的导弹火力，如果不能，它是否可以加强回应而不被拖入两条战线的全面冲突</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2023 03:55:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/hezbollahs-dangerous-plays-liable-to-spur-second-war-front-in-israels-north/0000018b-c555-dadd-abfb-e7ffb4530000</guid></item><item><title>反内塔尼亚胡右翼是击败他的关键</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-anti-bibi-ist-right-is-the-key-to-defeating-netanyahu/0000018b-c4d5-d25b-abdf-ddfd33700000</link><description>假设内塔尼亚胡在下次选举中坚持领导利库德集团，那么反对比比-卡汉主义轴心的集团现在应该已经集结了力量。否则，就会陷入给我们带来灾难的困境</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Nov 2023 22:30:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-anti-bibi-ist-right-is-the-key-to-defeating-netanyahu/0000018b-c4d5-d25b-abdf-ddfd33700000</guid></item><item><title>以色列左翼瞄准了错误的目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-israeli-left-is-aiming-at-the-wrong-target/0000018b-c4d4-df10-adeb-d6f6a1bf0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Nov 2023 22:26:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-israeli-left-is-aiming-at-the-wrong-target/0000018b-c4d4-df10-adeb-d6f6a1bf0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦权力机构是以色列的合作伙伴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/the-palestinian-authority-is-israels-partner/0000018b-c4d4-d25b-abdf-ddfda1550000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Nov 2023 22:25:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/the-palestinian-authority-is-israels-partner/0000018b-c4d4-d25b-abdf-ddfda1550000</guid></item><item><title>欧洲社会党领导人谴责哈马斯的暴行，支持以色列自卫权</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/europes-socialist-leaders-condemn-hamas-support-israels-right-to-defend-itself/0000018b-c4fd-d25b-abdf-ddfd97ce0000</link><description>在一份声明中，32个欧洲社会党在西班牙聚会的摘要中，各党派不要求限制以色列在加沙的军队活动，但警告不要发生“人道主义悲剧”，并呼吁暂停人道主义援助以缓解民众的处境</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Nov 2023 22:03:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-13/ty-article/.premium/europes-socialist-leaders-condemn-hamas-support-israels-right-to-defend-itself/0000018b-c4fd-d25b-abdf-ddfd97ce0000</guid></item><item><title>美国警告以色列不要在加沙希法医院的战斗中造成平民伤亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-12/ty-article/.premium/u-s-warns-israel-against-civilian-casualties-in-battle-at-al-shifa/0000018b-c537-dadd-abfb-e7ff78a70000</link><description>拜登政府对医院成为致命战斗现场的担忧是美国对加沙平民伤亡人数不断增加的更广泛担忧的一部分</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Nov 2023 21:53:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-12/ty-article/.premium/u-s-warns-israel-against-civilian-casualties-in-battle-at-al-shifa/0000018b-c537-dadd-abfb-e7ff78a70000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-12/ty-article/.premium/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-c579-d485-ab9b-ed7908b60000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Nov 2023 21:39:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-12/ty-article/.premium/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-c579-d485-ab9b-ed7908b60000</guid></item><item><title>数千名妇女在特拉维夫集会支持加沙的以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-12/ty-article/.premium/thousands-of-women-rally-in-tel-aviv-in-support-of-israeli-hostages-in-gaza/0000018b-c518-dadd-abfb-e7fe399f0000</link><description>示威者呼吁妇女和国际组织大声疾呼并谴责哈马斯劫持人质行为</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Nov 2023 20:44:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-12/ty-article/.premium/thousands-of-women-rally-in-tel-aviv-in-support-of-israeli-hostages-in-gaza/0000018b-c518-dadd-abfb-e7fe399f0000</guid></item><item><title>全世界的目光都集中在加沙，内塔尼亚胡也不能让美国人受气</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-12/ty-article/.highlight/with-the-worlds-eyes-on-gaza-netanyahu-cant-gaslight-americans-too/0000018b-c4b0-d485-ab9b-ecf1ebab0000</link><description>在两次接受美国媒体采访时，内塔尼亚胡向世界展示了以色列人长期以来所知道的事情：他的领导背后的整个作案方式已经消失，他现在实际上是一只借来的时间运作的跛脚鸭</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Nov 2023 18:16:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-12/ty-article/.highlight/with-the-worlds-eyes-on-gaza-netanyahu-cant-gaslight-americans-too/0000018b-c4b0-d485-ab9b-ecf1ebab0000</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，以色列和哈马斯可能几天后就释放加沙人质达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-12/ty-article/israel-hamas-deal-to-release-gaza-hostages-could-be-days-away-source-says/0000018b-c49a-db2f-a7cb-dedbcc920000</link><description>潜在的协议将使哈马斯释放数十名人质，以换取释放被关押在以色列的女性和青少年安全囚犯，但一名巴勒斯坦官员表示，谈判已因 Al-Shifa 医院附近的军事行动而暂停</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Nov 2023 18:12:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-12/ty-article/israel-hamas-deal-to-release-gaza-hostages-could-be-days-away-source-says/0000018b-c49a-db2f-a7cb-dedbcc920000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争紧张局势中，加拿大犹太学校再次遭枪击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/americas/2023-11-12/ty-article/shots-fired-at-canadian-jewish-school-again-amid-tensions-over-gaza-war/0000018b-c477-d485-ab9b-ec77b0af0000</link><description>蒙特利尔一所犹太学校在不到一周内第三次遭到枪击，据报道，康科迪亚大学冲突对立双方之间发生暴力争执，造成人员受伤和逮捕</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Nov 2023 17:56:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/americas/2023-11-12/ty-article/shots-fired-at-canadian-jewish-school-again-amid-tensions-over-gaza-war/0000018b-c477-d485-ab9b-ec77b0af0000</guid></item><item><title>这三个困境将决定以色列与哈马斯的战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-12/ty-article/.premium/these-three-dilemmas-will-determine-israels-war-with-hamas/0000018b-c444-df10-adeb-d6f603f80000</link><description>摧毁哈马斯的隧道还是拯救人质？归还加沙定居点还是将其移交给巴勒斯坦权力机构？优先打击哈马斯还是动员更多部队到真主党阵线？这些是以色列领导层必须做出的重大选择</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Nov 2023 16:49:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-12/ty-article/.premium/these-three-dilemmas-will-determine-israels-war-with-hamas/0000018b-c444-df10-adeb-d6f603f80000</guid></item></channel></rss>